\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Frobenius 方程具有以下形式 :
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{1}x_{1}+\cdots a_{n}x_{n}=m
\]

\end_inset

