\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{array}{c}
p^{\prime}=q+p\\
q^{\prime}+p^{\prime}=p
\end{array}\to\begin{array}{c}
q^{\prime}=-q\\
p^{\prime}=q+p
\end{array}
\]

\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $g_{n+1}=g_{n}p^{2}+(q+p)^{2n}$
\end_inset

中作代换
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
q^{\prime}=-q\\
p^{\prime}=p+q
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

得到
\begin_inset Formula $g_{n+1}=g_{n}\left(p+q\right)^{2}+p{}^{2n}$
